lyTime":"2020-05-18T18:53:17.000Z","msg":"好記得我拆釘果日企係到揀咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我耳仔好易敏感，拆完帶左佢哋對耳環一個月到諗住可以換靚靚耳環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知半日到就又紅又腫，耳針都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚇死我，如果你都易敏感既話，係街見到就算寫係防敏耳環都要小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a49e26732eedbe26ddfbce03da3fe755f945f1","tid":2023092,"uid":76105,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T19:12:17.000Z","msg":"第一次釘嘅款一定係柒，頭幾個月忍一忍有乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你即刻轉帶埋d didi Dom dom又唔知咩耳環，一陣發晒炎 流晒燶 你後悔都無用。<br />\n帶穩咗 2.3 個月，等個耳lon適應咗，往後十幾廿年話知你帶耳鏈耳鎖咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bda54137b8fb1c28d9184291c44042082422bb","tid":2023092,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39f714f22e788df7a042bb45c861d4ba5fcd5d35","tid":2023092,"uid":104254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfd56cff1aded4cb9894aac7539950db0d5cc708","tid":2023092,"uid":331827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"072abf7ea0ffab8eb9d1a3ff27c7e10fb72fbf9a","tid":2023092,"uid":104254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T18:39:09.000Z","msg":"我都係係mabelle釘，一開頭我都同你一樣肉痛買咗佢哋啲肉酸耳環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過依家無後悔到，因為真係無咁易敏感，你依段乖乖地時間帶多幾個月先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T18:48:07.000Z","msg":"原來唔係得我一個覺得佢哋嘅耳環唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T18:53:17.000Z","msg":"好記得我拆釘果日企係到揀咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我耳仔好易敏感，拆完帶左佢哋對耳環一個月到諗住可以換靚靚耳環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知半日到就又紅又腫，耳針都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚇死我，如果你都易敏感既話，係街見到就算寫係防敏耳環都要小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T19:44:15.000Z","msg":"唔知我個人問題定咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喺佢哋到釘完 <br />\n兩個耳窿都起肉粒 經常發炎狀態<br />\n最後頂唔順自己除咗，唔使一日就埋咗口<br />\n嗰陣都已經釘咗幾個月"},{"pid":"8947d488c7420b37556645adc3da8add865acf76","tid":2023092,"uid":217804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7831199eb7ee0a8fb928d250475301d0ed845ed","tid":2023092,"uid":331827,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"11e79c8c7fa7a4c385ea27256255e139f1c8aa29","tid":2023092,"uid":347768,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T18:26:04.000Z","msg":"我釘左十幾年 唔帶一排個洞都會慢慢生埋 <br />\n你唔想訓教un住又唔想埋左個耳窿可以考慮下帶透明耳針"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T18:31:05.000Z","msg":"收到，想問係唔係一定要過咗一年先可以戴吊嘅耳環"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:49:15.000Z","msg":"我九個月就戴緊吊嘅 但大前提係我三個月嘅時候一除 <br />\n跟住埋埋地口 嚇到我長期用耳針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 半年後先可以自己用到吊嘅耳環"},{"pid":"2785dce2c6a7af66ba461309c001f94818289028","tid":2023092,"uid":310908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:57:34.000Z","msg":"我之前穿左耳骨 <br />\n第五日發炎已經即刻自己拆出黎換耳針 <br />\n換左耳針之後個傷口就好快好番 <br />\n根本唔洗一個月已經隨便換其他耳環 <br />\n所以好推薦換左耳針先"},{"pid":"e00fa5aa2fdbacef9543159e513796d351158bb7","tid":2023092,"uid":127347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T01:03:31.000Z","msg":"細個讀書釘完一日就折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後入耳針痛到hihi"}]}